[code=geshi]procedure MultiText(Text: TStringArray);
var
  i, a: Integer;
begin
  for i:=0 to High(Text) do
  begin
    TypeSend(Text[i]);
    repeat
      a:=a+1;
      Wait(30+Random(51));
    Until(a>5);
  end;
end;[/code]

Simple code, yet some may find it useful. The usage is:[code=Geshi]
MultiText(['Text here', 'Text here']);[/code]
Of course, you can have as many sentences and you would like.

Here is a test file:[code=geshi]
{.include SRL\SRL.scar}
procedure MultiText(Text: TStringArray);
var
  i, a: Integer;
begin
  for i:=0 to High(Text) do
  begin
    TypeSend(Text[i]);
    repeat
      a:=a+1;
      Wait(30+Random(51));
    Until(a>5);
  end;
end;

begin
  MultiText(['Hello', 'what the', 'hi', 'this is multi-text', 'by IP-Drowner']);
end.[/code]

Enjoy ;)
